description: Pink, versatile deliciousness.  It’s perfect fried with eggs and wrapped like sushi and has made its way into countless dishes worldwide. But what other undiscovered possibilities does it have to bring more porky goodness into your life? Make sure you have SPAMMY …she’s never out of ideas.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, launch 'Spammy' and tell me a recipe
Alexa, launch 'Spammy' and get a recipe
name: SPAMMY!
shortDescription: Can’t get enough pink piggy deliciousness in your life? The SPAMMY skill will make sure you always have new ways to bring more porky goodness into your life.
